====================================================
Missoula Adoptables, <http://missoulaadoptables.org>
====================================================

Missoula Adoptables was created for Software Engineering at the University of
Montana-Missoula by Jon-Michael Deldin and Evan Cummings.

Requirements
------------

- PHP 5.2+
- MySQL 4.1+
- Apache with mod_rewrite (Lighty works without the pretty URLs)

Setup
-----

1. Clone the repository

    git clone git://github.com/jmdeldin/missoulaadoptables

2. Create a VirtualHost or move the repo to your htdocs directory

3. Create a database and import the SQL files in app/conf:

    mysql -u<user> -p <db_name> < setup.sql
    mysql -u<user> -p <db_name> < init-data.sql

4. Edit app/conf/conf.ini.dist and save it as app/conf/conf.ini


